Description: Handle of pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp? Uncertain symbol.
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.110, 24. It is not clear whether this is a separate entry or is to be taken with 25.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.1424)
